				<div class="col-md-12">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="about-we">
							<div class="col-md-9 col-sm-12">
								<div class="banner-title">
									<h2>Partner With Us</h2>
								</div>
								<div class="partner-intro">
									<%= image_tag 'partners-bg.png', :class => 'img-responsive', :alt => 'About Image' %>
								</div>
								<div class="vision-mission partner-inner-content">
									<div class="partner-content-description">
										<h2>Combining the forces for unlimited power online</h2>
										<p>The demand for Search Engine optimization &amp; marketing, web design &amp; development is skyrocketing. To keep current clients happy, many ad agencies, PR firms, web design and software companies have been forced to either learn the trade, hire SEO and PPC experts, or partner with firms that do it day-in and day-out. Many ad agencies either don't have the expertise, or the time to do search marketing for their clients.</p>
										<p>If you a Marketing, PR, Design, Programming, Multimedia, or Technical consulting firm, WebEnrich can offer your agency or company a strategic partnership to boost your client's online sales and reputation.</p>
										<p>That's because, we, at WebEnrich believe that when different domains get together, it's an illuminating experience that not only enhances our understanding of their functionalities but also helps us cater specifically to each domain. Partnering with a company from any domain but a professional as ours could have sparks fly. Now, doesn't that make you consider partnering with us?</p>
										<p>As you know that partnering can be very helpful if done with the right experience &amp; professional company, so let's combine the forces!</p>
										<p>WebEnrich offers your agency or company a strategic partnership to boost your client's online sales and reputation. </p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-3 col-sm-12">
								<div class="enquiry-form-part">
									<%= render 'layouts/widgets/quick_enquiry_form' %>
								</div>
								<div class="clients-slider hidden-sm">
									<%= render 'layouts/widgets/our_clients_single' %>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>